&lt;p data-pm-slice=&quot;1 1 []&quot;&gt;SLSQ227R268&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a Strategic Account Executive, you will own a flagship enterprise account and be accountable for a clear, executable strategy to exceed revenue, bookings, and consumption goals. You will execute with urgency and discipline, consistently overachieving targets while building deep, boardroom-level relationships and serving as a trusted Data &amp;amp; AI advisor to C-suite stakeholders.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Your mission is to drive sustained growth and deepen engagement within one of our most strategic customer partnerships in the region.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You’ll Do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own and execute an account strategy that accelerates revenue growth and drives increased platform consumption&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and maintain executive-level relationships, acting as a strategic advisor on Data &amp;amp; AI transformation&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Co-develop a comprehensive business plan with internal teams and ecosystem partners to exceed quarterly and annual bookings and consumption targets&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead customers, partners, and internal stakeholders to identify high-impact big data and AI use cases, proving business value on the Databricks Data Intelligence Platform&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive customer transformation through a coordinated approach that includes strategic partnerships, scoped professional services, training, and targeted executive engagement&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Orchestrate cross-functional teams to ensure customer success, long-term adoption, and expansion&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Impact You’ll Have&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Accelerate customer success by translating business priorities into measurable Data &amp;amp; AI outcomes&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Expand and deepen one of the company’s most strategic enterprise relationships&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Enable customers to realise tangible value from big data and AI initiatives at scale&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Consistently exceed revenue, booking, and consumption goals through disciplined execution and strategic leadership&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What We’re Looking For&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven experience managing large, global enterprise accounts and leading complex, multi-stakeholder sales cycles (retail experience preferred)&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Background in Big Data, Cloud, or SaaS environments&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Track record of exceeding quotas in high-growth enterprise software companies&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience driving usage- and commit-based engagement models&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong co-selling experience with cloud vendors and Global Systems Integrators&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrated ability to build executive business cases and secure C-level sponsorship&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Expertise in value-based selling within complex enterprise environments&lt;/li&gt;
